title: Right Hemisphere Deep UV Build 1309
description:
Deep UV is a breakthrough UV mapping technology for the creation and modification of UV mapping for n-polygonal models within an interactive 2D and 3D UV mapping environment.

With Deep UV you can:

    * Easily UV map 2D and 3D models
    * Use stand alone, or integrate workflows with plug-in support for existing DCC
      authoring applications

Whether you are a beginner or a professional 3D artist, Deep UV offers the best in UV mapping technology with both automatic and advanced features. Deep UV can be used standalone, or with Deep Paint 3D.
